nodes.text: Jeelvic was a male Jawa merchant who living during the Galactic War. He operated near the wreckage of the Stardream in the Dune Sea at the start of the Tatooine rakghoul pandemic. Later, he would wander into the rakghoul tunnels during subsequent outbreaks of the rakghoul plague on Alderaan, Tatooine, and Corellia.
